## Quick Start

```bash
# Frontend setup
cd web && npm install && npm run build && cd ..
go mod tidy

# Dev mode (frontend HMR + Go backend)
.\scripts\dev.ps1

# Build (outputs to deploy/linux, deploy/windows)
.\scripts\build.ps1
```

## Architecture

- **Frontend**: React + Vite + Tailwind CSS (SPA)
- **Backend**: Go HTTP server with `go:embed` (single binary)
- **Deploy**: Single executable serves both API and frontend
- **cmd/**: Each subdirectory is a separate binary (server, tools, etc.)

